<item>
            <title>[LU-14545] conf-sanity mount.lustre: mount /dev/loop1 at /tmp/t32/mnt/mdt1 failed: Cannot assign requested address</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14545</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On the &quot;failover pair&quot; Lustre configuration, like&lt;br/&gt;
    mds1_HOST=host1&lt;br/&gt;
    mds2_HOST=host2&lt;br/&gt;
    mds1failover_HOST=host2&lt;br/&gt;
    mds2failover_HOST=host1&lt;br/&gt;
fs2mdsdev can not be mounted on mds1_HOST because of fs2mdsdev has failover.node=&amp;lt;mds1_HOST&amp;gt;. Mount fails as:&lt;br/&gt;
    Denying initial registration attempt from nid &amp;lt;mds1_HOST&amp;gt;@tcp, specified as failover.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
